<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang='en'>
<head><meta charset='UTF-8'><meta name='viewport' content='width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0'><title>Teacher dashboard - TutorLink</title><link rel='stylesheet' href='/css/app.css'></head>
<body class='dashboard-page'>
    <nav class='nav shell'><a class='brand' href='/'><span class='brand-mark'>T</span>TutorLink</a><div class='user-nav'><b class='role-pill teacher-pill'>Teacher</b><span><strong><%= user.username %></strong><small><%= user.email %></small></span><a class='button secondary' href='/logout'>Log out</a></div></nav>
    <main class='dashboard shell'>
        <% if (errorMessages.length) { %><div class='alert error'><%= errorMessages.join(' ') %></div><% } %>
        <% if (successMessages.length) { %><div class='alert success'><%= successMessages.join(' ') %></div><% } %>
        <header class='dashboard-header'><div><span class='eyebrow'>Teacher workspace</span><h1>Ready to make an impact, <%= user.username.split(' ')[0] %>?</h1><p>Your dedicated space for guiding students and organising teaching.</p></div><div class='profile-mark teacher-avatar'>TC</div></header>
        <section class='welcome teacher-welcome'><h2>Help every learner find their next step.</h2><p>This protected dashboard is available only to accounts with the Teacher role.</p></section>
        <section class='action-grid'>
            <article><span>01</span><h3>Teaching opportunities</h3><p>Review sessions and apply where your expertise is the best fit.</p><a class='button secondary' href='/teacher/sessions' style='margin-top:1rem; display:inline-block; text-decoration:none;'>Browse Sessions</a></article>
            <article><span>02</span><h3>My applications</h3><p>Keep upcoming sessions and commitments visible in one place.</p><a class='button secondary' href='/teacher/my-applications' style='margin-top:1rem; display:inline-block; text-decoration:none;'>My Applications</a></article>
            <article><span>03</span><h3>Student support</h3><p>Maintain a clear view of the learners you guide.</p></article>
        </section>
    </main>
</body>
</html>
